<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/big_ramy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Mamdouh Elssbiay</a>, better known as <em>Big Ramy</em>, is an Egyptian mass monster who holds two consecutive Olympia titles. As you can probably guess by his nickname, he’s one of the biggest bodybuilders ever to have walked on stage. At 5′9″ tall with 300 pounds of stage weight, he certainly has a lot of muscle on his frame.&nbsp;</p>



<p>While he is still renowned for his sheer size and mass, he hasn&#8217;t competed since the 2022 Mr. Olympia. We’re not sure what the future holds for this mass monster.</p>



